A '''crackhead''' is a person who is [[drug addiction|addicted]] to [[crack cocaine]]. 

==Usage==
Ryan Goecke is a Crackhead.

==History==
"Crackheads" appeared in great numbers during the [[1980s]], as crack cocaine became more available, cheaper, and of higher potency than other forms of [[cocaine]]. Crack addicts were and are a largely [[urban area|urban]] phenomenon. 

